pageFunctionResult.decsription: India’s Prime Minister Priyamvada Thakur is losing popularity with the voters. Her secretary Ashok Pandey suggests a wild strategy to help gain some political advantage. Guess who comes to the rescue? Fashionista and NRI Tanya Bansal. From the population of over a billion people, what makes Tanya a perfect candidate?
pageFunctionResult.title: And The Job Of A Lifetime...

pageFunctionResult.decsription: By-elections are announced, and Tanya Thakur is set to contest the elections from Sumerpur. Her campaigning begins on a disastrous note, and she decides to leave the country, but not before organizing a one of a kind fashion show. Her grandma Priyamvada Thakur couldn’t be more horrified.
pageFunctionResult.title: And The Best Selfie Ever...

pageFunctionResult.decsription: India’s youngest PM Tanya Thakur takes the oath in her own style. As soon as she takes office, a slew of issues awaits the PM’s immediate attention. Peace talks with neighbouring countries, South Asian Summit, terrorism and, of course, the wrath of the opposition are just few issues of national importance. But before that, PM Tanya has a crazy and controversial request.
pageFunctionResult.title: And Love Thy Neighbour..

pageFunctionResult.decsription: The leaders of South Asian countries reach India. PM Tanya Thakur plays a fine host. But the huge task before her is to get the leaders to sign a crucial peace treaty. What will Tanya do to bring some peace in the region? Meanwhile, former PM Priyamvada Thakur is getting increasingly worried over Tanya’s antics.
pageFunctionResult.title: And Force Thy Neighbour To Love You..

pageFunctionResult.decsription: What does it take to change a law in the largest democracy of the world? Next issue on PM Tanya’s agenda is a law that needs to be changed. But before she can introduce the bill in the parliament, she must take care of some internal opposition. Enter Swamiji, grandma’s trusted and revered aid. What will Priyamvada Thakur do to stop Tanya?
pageFunctionResult.title: And It's Time To Create History

pageFunctionResult.decsription: PM Tanya Thakur is not the one to back down. She does what she is best at - being all over social media. But whether she trends for the right reasons or not, that’s for India to decide. However, Indian politicians and fellow MPs don’t show any signs of warming up to her ways. Are Tanya’s trendy and fashionable ideas putting the future of Indian democracy in jeopardy?
pageFunctionResult.title: And The Coming Out Party...

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Throughout her short but eventful political stint, PM Tanya also gains few enemies along with millions of followers. While Tanya makes exciting date plans with Sachin, grandma Priyamvada Thakur hatches a sinister plan to secure her Prime Ministerial candidature for the next elections. Stakes are high in this battle between the grandma and the granddaughter.
pageFunctionResult.title: Season Finale : And The High Hook-UP...

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Three months have passed since Karan and Tipsy last saw each other. Tipsy is busy fulfilling her to-do list in Europe. But is she happy? Before she can figure this out, Sherry calls her back to Mumbai urgently. Tipsy is shocked to see Karan at a local court. Will she ignore him or talk to him?
pageFunctionResult.title: Pal Pal Dil Ke Paas

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan Khanna tries to understand and get close to Tipsy. But he fears what will happen when Tipsy learns that Radhika is living with him. To Karan’s delight, Tipsy unites with him to solve Sherry and Vishal’s problems. However, Karan is less than delighted to see Tipsy meet her ‘date’ at a café.
pageFunctionResult.title: Ae Dil Hai Mushkil

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Chitti and Amma arrive at the airport and Karan hopes to impress them. But its not easy to impress Chitti. While shopping, Trisha is accused of shoplifting and an unlikely messiah comes to her rescue. Radhika’s legal battle for Prabuddha’s property is set to get more complicated.
pageFunctionResult.title: Pehla Nasha

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Romila is back! And so is more drama in Karan’s life. Will this create more distance between Karan and Tipsy or bring them closer? Meanwhile, Palash discusses his past with Karan even as he risks crossing paths with it. In her next meeting with Palash, Radhika brings Karan along with her. Will Karan and Palash continue to remain friends?
pageFunctionResult.title: Kambakht Ishq

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Radhika and Karan’s meeting with Palash doesn’t go well. Karan accuses him of being cold-hearted. In his attempt to impress Chitti, Vishal gets trashed, literally. Complicating matters further, Chitti considers who among Vishal and Addu is a suitable match for Tipsy. Even though Radhika decides to move out of Karan’s house, the distance between Tipsy and Karan increases.
pageFunctionResult.title: Pyar Tune Kya Kiya

pageFunctionResult.decsription: This is the season of confrontations for Tipsy and Karan. Tipsy wants to know what does Radhika mean to Karan? An upset Tipsy meets Addu and Karan walks in. He gets more upset in return. When Tipsy visits Karan’s home to placate him, she is not ready for what she sees.
pageFunctionResult.title: Dil Hai Ki Maanta Nahin

pageFunctionResult.decsription: In a hilarious turn of events, a newly married Sherry meets another prospective groom. Vishal is having a hard time handling the situation. Tipsy’s apartment turns into a headquarter of chaos. At Trisha’s birthday party, the photo booth captures not just pictures but some major drama. Rohan learns something that Trisha has been over-looking all these days.
pageFunctionResult.title: Baaton Baaton Mein

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Tipsy and Karan get an opportunity to spend some time alone as Amma and Chitti are not at home. But will they make this moment special? Karan rushes to help Radhika get her boutique back. But Palash refuses every amicable proposal. Tipsy’s new patient is admitted in a serious condition.
pageFunctionResult.title: Hamari Adhuri Kahani

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Palash battles for his life and Tipsy tries her best to save him. She fears getting dragged into his complicated life. She contemplates telling Karan all about her past. Will he understand? Palash pulls an elaborate plan to get close to Tipsy.
pageFunctionResult.title: Jiya Laage Na Tum Bin

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Tipsy experiences shock and delight simultaneously at the inauguration event of Veda Rehab Clinic as Palash and Karan both present themselves. The event proves to be a moment of bitter realization for both the men. Tipsy is left hurt and upset. An adamant Palash offers a deal that leaves Karan fuming. What is the future of Karan and Tipsy?
pageFunctionResult.title: Jab Koi Baat Bigad Jaye

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan wants to help Tipsy but is unable to and on the other hand Tipsy wants to talk about Palash but can’t get herself to do it.  She fears that their respective past is preventing their future from taking any shape. To make matters worse, Palash plots to keep the two apart.  Meanwhile, Radhika doesn’t answer calls from her anyone.
pageFunctionResult.title: Picture Abhi Baaki Hai

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Amidst the wedding celebrations, Karan is nursing his broken heart. He decides to leave, but not before making Chitti realise her mistake. When Sherry confronts Tipsy about her shocking decision, she shows no signs of changing her mind. But there is something that Tipsy wants Karan to know. Will Tipsy manage to talk to Karan before he leaves?
pageFunctionResult.title: Aa Gale Lag Ja

pageFunctionResult.decsription: In a surprising turn of events, several hearts unite. Tipsy and Karan have made many sacrifices but finally declare their love for each other. Is this the beginning of a beautiful journey for Karan and Tipsy? Meanwhile, Trisha has other plans for her parents, Karan and Radhika.
pageFunctionResult.title: Season Finale: Kya Yahi Pyar Hai

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Artists don’t compromise with their art. But what about lovers? Do they compromise with their heart? Ananya, a talented interior designer, craves nothing more than Rohit’s company. To mark three years of togetherness, they meet for a quiet celebration. But nothing goes according to plan.
pageFunctionResult.title: He Loves Me, He Loves Me Not

pageFunctionResult.decsription: The two different worlds of Rohit Mehra collide with each other when his daughter, Bani, confronts him about Ananya. It seems Rohit will have to make a choice, as Ananya drifts apart from him. His wife, Poonam, offers him a second chance. Will Rohit be forced accept it?
pageFunctionResult.title: Memories, Magic and Madness

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Whenever a heart breaks, no matter how young or old, the grief is the same. Poonam is devasted because this time her husband, Rohit, can’t forget Ananya. Rohit feels a certain guilt, but Ananya doesn’t wish to share the burden of this guilt. Meanwhile, Bani refuses to marry her long-time boyfriend Arya.
pageFunctionResult.title: Desperate Love, Guilty Heart

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Is Ananya and Rohit’s relationship ready to reveal itself to the world? Maybe not. But Ananya is tired of hiding their beautiful love from the world. Rohit arrives at a wedding function with his family but leaves the venue without them. This leaves his family and all the guests stunned. Meanwhile, Nikki and Bani try to secretly find out the identity of the other woman in their dad’s life.
pageFunctionResult.title: Who Am I To You?

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Love and life is getting increasingly suffocating for Ananya. To escape all of this, she leaves the city. Rohit desperately searches for her all over. With a motive in mind, Bani agrees to marry her boyfriend Arya. Poonam is delighted with her daughter’s decision. But, her delight is short-lived when she learns about Rohit’s decision.
pageFunctionResult.title: Stolen Love

pageFunctionResult.decsription: When the storm of divorce hits the Mehras, they are shattered. Poonam reluctantly accepts this bitter truth, while making a heartfelt appeal to Rohit.  What is driving Rohit to seek divorce from Poonam? Is it something he truly desires or is it just to keep Ananya happy? Meanwhile, Bani reaches Ananya’s house and is not ready for what she discovers.
pageFunctionResult.title: Always An Outsider

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Is it better to live a lie for the sake of society or embrace truth for your own peace? Rohit and Poonam are divided on matters of marriage and relations. Before Rohit can get a divorce from Poonam he must fulfill her nearly impossible demand. Ananya is delighted when Rohit moves in with her. But it takes only one phone call from Poonam for him to return home and attend to his family.
pageFunctionResult.title: The Wife's Challenge

pageFunctionResult.decsription: With immense pain, Poonam and her family try to face the divorce proceedings with some dignity. But there is no dignity for Ananya in fulfilling Rohit’s request, even though she is hopeful and happy with Rohit moving in. Will Poonam and Rohit legally put an end to their marriage?
pageFunctionResult.title: Mine. Forever

pageFunctionResult.decsription: When two people divorce, is it right to put the blame on a third person? Nevertheless, Ananya blames herself for the pain of Poonam and her daughters. Rohit tries to meet his family, but he reaches home to find it empty. On the other hand, Nikki and Bani have a plan to get their father to realise his “mistake”.
pageFunctionResult.title: Love or 'Tug-O'-War'

pageFunctionResult.decsription: After a long time, Poonam sees a ray of happiness, as the Mehras gear up for celebrations. For Rohit, Bani’s wedding is an opportunity to spend much needed quality time with his family. But arrival of Sheena Masi adds some unexpected colours to the occasion. Will Poonam and Rohit come closer?
pageFunctionResult.title: J For Jealousy

pageFunctionResult.decsription: In between all the preparations and celebrations Rohit misses Ananya each and every moment. Ananya patiently waits for a call or a message from Rohit, but she is left disappointed. Sheena Masi’s latest idea proves to be a masterstroke. What will Rohit do to save his relationship with Ananya?
pageFunctionResult.title: Trials and Tribulations

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Everyone celebrates Bani and Arya’s union with lots of song and dance. All the guests have a blast on the dance floor. Over a drink or two, a little more than light hearted gossip is shared. How will the Mehras cope with the latest shocking development?
pageFunctionResult.title: Crossing Boundaries

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Bani gets married and so does Rohit. An excited Ananya moves in with Rohit to start a new chapter of her life with the love of her life. But Rohit is still mad at Ananya and her friends. What will Ananya do to get Rohit to talk to her? When Rohit doesn’t show up at his own party Ananya is going be heart-broken yet again.
pageFunctionResult.title: Home Alone

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Some time has passed since Ananya, Rohit and Poonam’s lives changed forever. Ananya is almost satisfied with her life with Rohit, and Poonam is beginning to discover a new way of life. Ananya craves for something more than just being a wife. But she struggles to express her feelings to Rohit who seem to be increasingly getting drawn to his family like never before.
pageFunctionResult.title: New Beginnings Old Ghosts

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Though Poonam has accepted a life without Rohit, Ananya is yet to find acceptance with Rohit’s family. A medical emergency leads to Bani’s hospitalization. It is a moment for Rohit to reflect upon his priorities in life. For Ananya, it will be a choice between her career and companionship.
pageFunctionResult.title: Season Finale : Nothing Lasts Forever

pageFunctionResult.decsription: More than just beauty, life and reality of Kashmir will reveal itself through the eyes of the Mirza sisters, Meher, Jannat, Bahira, and Amal. At a wedding function, the familial bonds of the Mirzas are put to test when Aunt Fatima becomes the subject of gossip and discussions. Love not only hurts but also insults.
pageFunctionResult.title: The Mirza Girls

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Someone’s love is everyone’s trouble. The Mirza family is castigated for the actions of Fatima. This outrages Jannat. Tabish Azad unwittingly plants a dangerous idea in her head to answer back. At the job interview, Meher has an unpleasant encounter with Dr. Naushad Rizvi, who questions the Mirza family’s morals. The trying times have just begun.
pageFunctionResult.title: The Imperfect Affair

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Jannat Mirza’s blog and Amal Mirza’s photographs become a cause for concern for the Mirza Family. In a complicated entanglement of politics and love, Fatima risks facing dejection. Jannat’s blogpost creates waves in the valley. How will she justify her writings? Meanwhile, Meher hears some unsavoury tales about Dr. Naushad Rizvi.
pageFunctionResult.title: Blogs for Dogs

pageFunctionResult.decsription: After committing a mistake, Meher contemplates quitting her job at the Rizvi hospital. It’s Tabish’s birthday and time to party. The party becomes a platform for Bahira’s band Jashn to give their first ever public performance. Tabish tries to express his love and Meher spends the evening morose and deep in thought. What will happen when another unexpected guest arrives at the party?
pageFunctionResult.title: Jashn!

pageFunctionResult.decsription: At the party, a drunk Meher bumps into Dr. Naushad Rizvi and unknowingly reveals almost all that ails her.  Bahira Mirza’s musical performance goes viral all over the internet. It not only creates ripples in Kahsmir but in the whole country. Mirza family couldn’t be any prouder of her. There is another side to Dr. Naushad Rizvi, Meher finds out.
pageFunctionResult.title: Gone Viral

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Most find music soothing, but some find it infuriating. As Bahira begins to discover herself through her soulful music, along the way her band Jashn gains not just fans but also few fanatics. Soon the whole family will find themselves in the center of this new turmoil. Will new rumours at the hospital bring Meher and Dr. Naushad closer?
pageFunctionResult.title: Fans and Fanatics

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Bahira Mirza is nervous yet looks forward to Jashn’s first ever charity concert. But what doesn’t begin well can never end well. Bahira and her band members are forced off the stage even before they begin. In a mad scramble the Mirza sisters fear losing their sister. Meanwhile, Aunt Fatima is forced to choose between her family and love.
pageFunctionResult.title: Stuck Between Heaven And Hell

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Just when things were starting to look positive between Meher and Naushad, their present and past becomes a cause of friction between the two. The identity of Jannat Mirza’s blog comes to light. Could Salman Baig be behind it? How long can Jannat Mirza continue to write?  The family will bond closer and stronger.
pageFunctionResult.title: Main Kashmir Hoon

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Kashmir is not ready for Jannat Mirza’s fiery pen as she is forced to pay a heavy price for her aggressive blogposts. Dr. Naushad Rizvi is devastated to see his daughter, Alia, taken seriously ill. Meher attends to Alia and extends much needed support to Naushad. But despite this, why does the wall between the two remain unbroken? Meanwhile, there is a new guest in town.
pageFunctionResult.title: Conflict Zones

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Jannat is awestruck with the new guest. This doesn’t go down well with Tabish. Bahira’s life is more and more in danger even as her band Jashn is gaining more popularity. Meher is forced to take a much closer look at the complications of her own personal life. Will this create more distance between Naushad and Meher or bring them closer?
pageFunctionResult.title: Of Hope And Fatwas

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Despite the threat of Fatwa looming over Bano, Raghu continues to film his documentary. Jannat and Raghu schedule an interview meeting with the staunch Islamic leader Mohammad Altaaf. What will Mohammad Altaaf reveal? Will it be worth risking their lives? Meanwhile, Dr. Naushad Rizvi invites Meher to his home.
pageFunctionResult.title: Surgical Strike

pageFunctionResult.decsription: A new relationship is developing between Raghu and Jannat. But the bond between the four sisters seems to be breaking apart. The fear, jealousy, and complications of life are taking a toll on everyone. An unfortunate development about their father’s whereabouts doesn’t help either.
pageFunctionResult.title: Accidental Coincidences

pageFunctionResult.decsription: It’s the beginning of holy Ramzan, along with everything good and pure that comes with it. The Mirzas gather with their friends and family for a grand Iftar. The gathering is witness to jovial conversations as well as intense emotions. Fatima realizes and embraces a new definition of love, and Meher develops new feelings for Dr. Naushad. But Tabish and Jannat’s friendship risks falling apart.
pageFunctionResult.title: Waqt-e-Sehar

pageFunctionResult.decsription: The events at the Iftar gathering have left many with a bruised heart. Raghu is accused of committing a heinous act by Amal, and Jannat is torn between the two. What is the truth and who is a liar? Meher and Naushad discover each other and open their hearts just a little. But will Meher’s past also open her old wounds?
pageFunctionResult.title: Too Close For Comfort

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Jannat tries to sort out the unfortunate aftermath of the Iftar party. She deeply cares for her sister Amal, but at the same time, doesn’t want to lose Raghu. Do Raghu and Jannat have any chance at a shared future? The more Meher tries to run away from her past the more it catches up with her. Not only her old wounds open, but it seems like she may be scarred forever.
pageFunctionResult.title: Straight To Hell

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Bruised and hurt, Meher is completely shattered. Her sisters try to be the much-needed pillars of support. But Jannat is not ready to back down. What will be the consequences when Jannat takes matters in her own hand? Even Naushad is hurt seeing Meher blatantly lie to him.
pageFunctionResult.title: Hide and Seek

pageFunctionResult.decsription: These are trying times for the Mirza sisters. Lying seems to be the only way. But Aunt Fatima has her suspicions. She is determined to figure out the reason behind the sisters’ silence. Naushad sees Fatima’s mehndi ceremony as an opportunity to share his feelings with Meher. Will Naushad bring some new hope in Meher’s life?
pageFunctionResult.title: Aakhri Aafreen

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Favourite aunt of Mirza sisters, Aunt Fatima is getting married. Tabish finally confesses his love to Jannat but gets an unexpected reaction from her. On the other hand, Naushad only comes close to confessing his feelings to Meher. Many words remain unsaid as some shocking allegations captivate the guests at the wedding.
pageFunctionResult.title: Breathless

pageFunctionResult.decsription: As the turmoil in Kashmir rises, the fragile dreams of the Mirza sisters get caught up in the storm. But Bahira and Amal desperately hold onto their dreams close to their hearts. Will the Mirzas be able to separate their future from that of Kashmir’s?
pageFunctionResult.title: Alvida

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Once upon a time there was life, full of desires and dreams. Now there is only a trace of what used to be. This is the real Kashmir. The beautiful valleys and picturesque mountains hides within them the deep sorrows of its people. It resides firmly in the hearts of Mirzas.
pageFunctionResult.title: Season Finale : End Of The Beginning

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Dhara and Shivam are tech addicts and lovers of social media. The plan is to watch some Cricket and click lots of selfies. More than a hundred pictures and multiple poses later, they manage to find the perfect snap. But a goof up of epic proportions by Shivam ruins that perfect selfie.
pageFunctionResult.title: Say Cheese

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Dhara loves to cook for Shivam. And Shivam loves to share his food with his colleagues. As Dhara prepares a special meal, she accidently discovers the real reason behind Shivam’s empty tiffin box.
pageFunctionResult.title: Bhadwa Baigan

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Dhara thinks Shivam is getting lazier by the day, since he prefers sleep over workout. With a fit-bit on her wrist and a smartphone in her pocket, Dhara goes for a nice long run on her own. But on returning, she is shocked to find some bizarre activity on Shivam’s phone.
pageFunctionResult.title: I Wanna Exercise

pageFunctionResult.decsription: It’s Sunday! Shivam and Dhara prefer to spend their Sunday chilling at home. But when work calls, Dhara doesn’t mind attending to it. At the end of the day she ends up taking care of more than just work. Should Shivam be worried?
pageFunctionResult.title: Thodi Cute Thodi Sweet

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Party time is equal to fun time. Shivam and Dhara head for an evening with old friends. This tech dependent couple will soon realise that when alcohol flows, even technology doesn’t come to the rescue.
pageFunctionResult.title: Daru Daru Daru

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Post the previous night’s drinking session, Dhara and Shivam cure the hangover in their own unique way. Their day becomes all about a little blame game, some pictures, and one big galti se mis-tech.
pageFunctionResult.title: Hangover

pageFunctionResult.decsription: While chatting on an instant messaging app with her little brother, Dhara gets the shock of her life. Will Dhara and Shivam handle this situation virtually or in real time?
pageFunctionResult.title: Happy & Gay

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Dhara can’t wait to flaunt her brand-new outfit at a friend’s wedding. Shivam has taken complete charge of finding the exact location of the venue, thanks to Google Maps. Which direction will Google Maps take them?
pageFunctionResult.title: Chaddi Ki Shaadi

pageFunctionResult.decsription: An arrogant, fading superstar, and a humble, caring doctor – does destiny have its own plans for them?
pageFunctionResult.title: Do Akele Shehar Mein

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan’s last effort to revive his career lands him in front of an unintimidated Tripura. Will they get along?
pageFunctionResult.title: Kabhi Haan Kabhi Naa

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Tripura is at her professional best. But she’s not prepared for Karan’s plans for her. Will they find some common ground?
pageFunctionResult.title: Humsafar

pageFunctionResult.decsription: A questionable character, a failed marriage, and an estranged daughter. The arrogant actor has his own reasons to frown while Tripura struggles with a case of mistaken identity.
pageFunctionResult.title: Pati Patni Aur Woh

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Trisha’s bitterness hurts Karan. A meltdown takes him to his extremes. Will Tripura be able to pull him back from the edge?
pageFunctionResult.title: Khel Khel Mein

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Tripura foils Karan’s escape plan. How long will the alcoholic avoid his therapist?
pageFunctionResult.title: Bairi Piya

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan comes to Tripura’s rescue. But there is a hidden price to it. Will Tripura be able to handle it?
pageFunctionResult.title: Bandini

pageFunctionResult.decsription: A confrontation, followed by a fallout, followed by a surprise visit from a very important person. Karan and Tripura both begin to discover new sides of each other’s personalities.
pageFunctionResult.title: Aur Pyaar Ho Gaya

pageFunctionResult.decsription: As Karan tries to set things right with Tipsy, things take a strange turn as she misinterprets his honest intentions.
pageFunctionResult.title: Uff Yeh Mohabbat

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan’s closeness to Tripura’s family leaves her awestruck. Will she go with the flow or will Karan hit a dead end?
pageFunctionResult.title: Pyar Ke Side Effects

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan’s feelings for Tripura lend a new meaning to his life. Is this the beginning of a love story or is Karan headed for another disappointment?
pageFunctionResult.title: Ek Ladki Ko Dekha

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan vows to unite with the love of his life. Will Tripura be able to understand her own feelings towards Karan?
pageFunctionResult.title: Kissa Angoothi Ka

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Two men in love with the same woman. Who will win her heart? Will Karan give up so easily?
pageFunctionResult.title: Dulhan Hum Le Jayenge

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Tripura defends Karan in front of his family. Will this mark the beginning of their love story?
pageFunctionResult.title: Kuch Na Kaho

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Karan is faced with a sudden choice between love and unforeseen responsibilities. Will this be the end of Karan and Tipsy's newfound understanding?
pageFunctionResult.title: Season Finale : Hum Tum

pageFunctionResult.decsription: It's merit vs. bias for Captain Shikha Sharma. How long before she’s recognized for her strength rather than her gender?
pageFunctionResult.title: The Beginning

pageFunctionResult.decsription: At the obstacles training ground, under Naik Subedar Bhatti’s watch, the officers sweat it out to finish the obstacles task in the given time. Almost everyone expects Capt. Sharma to fail but she is determined to prove otherwise. Meanwhile, in the first week someone is forced to exit the course.
pageFunctionResult.title: The Outsider

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Though accounts of Capt. Sharma’s endurance reaches the Defense Ministry, only ‘Dozakh’ will be the ultimate test. Tensions between Capt. Rathore and Capt. Sharma increase when he is punished for reporting late next morning. But the commando training is not just hard work, the officers get an evening to relax and enjoy. Capt. Sharma gives everyone the slip to go away for a while.
pageFunctionResult.title: The Player

pageFunctionResult.decsription: With a past heavily looming over her psyche, Capt. Shikha Sharma endures it all in the Dozakh task. Capt. Siddiqui gets upset when Sharma refuses to discuss her personal life with him. Meanwhile, Col. Ajinkya Sathe pulls a surprise by suddenly changing a decision. Who will be Shikha Sharma’s allies in the final task of Dozakh? One more will bite the dust.
pageFunctionResult.title: Heart Of Darkness Part 1

pageFunctionResult.decsription: How far can a human body push its limits to prove a statement? Can you really keep quite while going through hell? Now, Dozakh is not just a task to be completed but a real mission to be accomplished. Due to puzzling circumstances, team leader Capt. Shikha Sharma’s leadership skills are questioned by her team member. This is a ticking time bomb.
pageFunctionResult.title: Heart Of Darkness - Part 2

pageFunctionResult.decsription: The final task may be officially over, but it is the beginning of new struggles for Capt. Shikha Sharma. Leaving SFTC seems like the only option. The officers submit debrief reports about everything that happened during the operation. What will the reports of Team Alpha reveal? Gen. Ramani appoints a trusted officer to investigate.
pageFunctionResult.title: Down But Not Out

pageFunctionResult.decsription: What happened that day? Why did Capt. Siddiqui go home and why is Capt. Shikha Sharma in the hospital? Col. Imtiaz Hussain is here to find some answers, and members of Team Alpha are concerned.  He begins by interrogating RMO Capt. Aparna Rao. Is she hiding the truth? Meanwhile, Shikha Sharma submits her debrief report.
pageFunctionResult.title: Mind Games

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Lt. Col. Imtiaz Hussain approaches Shikha Sharma to find out her version of the events. Shikha Sharma learns a few things that bring some clarity. How long before she finds out the ultimate truth? Meanwhile Capt. Bilal Siddiqui talks to Lt. Col. Imtiaz Hussain.
pageFunctionResult.title: Prisoners of Conscience

pageFunctionResult.decsription: Lt. Col Imtiaz Hussain figures out the actual sequence of events of that fateful day. Col. Ajinkya Sathe is outraged after learning the findings of the investigation. Moreover, he finds Shikha Sharma’s decision more shocking. The final two exercises of the course begin. Find out why Shikha Sharma eyes for the 3rd spot and not the 1st.
pageFunctionResult.title: The confession

pageFunctionResult.decsription: The remaining officers successfully complete the course and pass out wearing the Maroon Beret. They are now part of the elite of the elite forces. Along with the rescue operation Capt. Shikha Sharma also finishes another very important operation.  Will Capt. Shika Sharma create history?
pageFunctionResult.title: Season Finale : What goes around... comes around
